title: Ep. 612 - A Search For Jetha - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal and Bhide get into a huge fight post which Bhide tells this to Bhau Kaka. Bhau Kaka comes with his men and looks for Jethalal.

title: Ep. 613 - Bhau Kaka Serves Aam Ras - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhau Kaka is happy to see the togetherness in Gokuldham. He serves the Aam ras he had got from Ratnagiri. Finally, Jethalal and Bhide's issue resolves and they gel well again.

title: Ep. 614 - Tapu Sena Wants A Cricket Kit - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu Sena gets training from Rahul. They ask for a cricket kit to play to which the parents refuse.

title: Ep. 615 - Tapu On A Mission - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu Sena plans to make everyone agree to their demand. Parents sternly refuse to get them a cricket kit. Tapu comes up with an idea.

title: Ep. 616 - Tapu Sena On A Hunger Strike - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu and friends inform everyone that they will be on a hunger strike until their demands are fulfilled. They eat a lot of wafers and chips before they start on with the hunger strike. Tapu Sena set up a tent.

title: Ep. 617 - Sodhi Has A Plan - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The hunger strike continues. Tapu Sena is adamantly standing by their protest. Sodhi comes up with a plan and suggests everyone bribe them with gifts so that they end their hunger strike.

title: Ep. 618 - Scheme Fails Miserably - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal and friends reveal the deal to Tapu Sena. Tapu Sena thinks of accepting the deal but will still be on a hunger strike. While people discuss how to deal with this situation, Tapu faints.

title: Ep. 619 - Media Covers The News - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Society of Gokuldham gets to know that Tapu was just acting to be unconscious. A reporter comes to cover the news of children on a hunger strike. Jethalal asks Daya to make Gulab Jamun.

title: Ep. 620 - Jethalal's Success - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal learns a lesson of solving one's problem on his own. Tapu Sena breaks their hunger strike and eats the gulab jamun. Tapu hits someone's car which later turns out to be Salman Khan's car.

title: Ep. 621 - Salman Khan Comes To Gokuldham - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Salman Khan pays a visit to Gokuldham. He tries to persuade the people to let their children play on the ground if not in society. He gifts a season cricket kit to Tapu Sena. Salman promotes his film.

title: Ep. 622 - Dancing To Tunes - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Gokuldham dances to the tunes with Salman Khan. Daya wishes to share her experience of meeting Salman Khan with Sundar and her mother. Tapu Sena is happy as they could play with season ball in the ground.

title: Ep. 623 - Vacation Plan - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal and friends decide to go on a vacation. Everyone cancels in unison. Later, Champaklal and Tapu Sena decides to set up a Gokuldham Khel Mahotsav. A judge to be called to decide on the winners.

title: Ep. 624 - Sundar Comes Home - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Gada family shares their past memories of taking part in sports. Sundar comes to Gokuldham from Ahmedabad. He taunts Jethalal for his overweight body and challenges him to win any sport. Jethalal goes for excercise early morning.

title: Ep. 625 - Gokuldham Gets Ready For Mahotsav - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Society gears up for the Gokuldham Khel Mahotsav. Everyone starts practicing for the mini Olympic games. Sundar takes care of the decoration and lighting. It would be interesting to know who would be the judge for the Mahotsav.

title: Ep. 626 - Jethalal Is Shocked To Know The Judges - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Reporter Ritu covers the news of interviewing the players for tonight. Champaklal discloses the judges for the Mahotsav. Jethalal is shocked to know who the judges are. Judges tell them about the first competition and explain the rules.
